snippet.title: Formula Retro Racing Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist it now on Steam https://store.steampowered.com/app/1239660/Formula_Retro_Racing/

Formula Retro Racing is a retro style arcade racing game that’s influenced by the classic arcade racing games of the early 90’s.

Coming soon to Steam and Xbox One.

More info on our Website
http://repixel8.com/formula-retro-racing
